</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C96F4116358FDA6162760A1C71C26AF1" pageId="107" pageNumber="108" type="range">
<paragraph id="976FA3D06DECC48FBAE44D56F5AD0A7F" pageId="107" pageNumber="108">Range.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="17AACC1D1C05992E79B232EED124319C" pageId="107" pageNumber="108">Southeastern Europe to South Asia. Also naturalized, and widespread in cultivation.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
